verbose_text: By contrast, in uninfected, dual humanized mice and hepatocyte transplanted mice, ALB levels increased to a median value of 336 mug/ml (range 117.6-2663 mug/ml) and 708 mug/ml (range 148.7-1215.7 mug/ml) post-sham infection from their median values of 196 mug/ml (range 48.4-503 mug/ml) and 227 mug/ml (range 50-828.5 mug/ml), respectively (XREF_FIG B).
